column1:
Whew, this summer
sure is a hot one.
Man, the curry there is so good.
Another police scandal? There've been so many lately.
Hey, let's go see what's playing at the movies!
Is it true that the Phantom Thieves are back?
Their Desires were stolen? What does that even mean?
What a commotion...
Now things are really getting interesting!
The Phantom Thieves are back? How intriguing.
I knew that sudden confession was fishy...
Aliiice! Make me your slave!
*sigh* Oh, Alice...
I can't stop thinking about her. I just love her so much!
I wanna be just like Alice...
I can't believe Alice touched me... I'm never washing this hand again!
Alice's CD got sold out everywhere...
Alice is the cutest person in the universe!
Alice has such an incredible fashion sense!

That document tampering
confession... I heard it was
the Phantom Thieves.
Is she really that cute?
Hello? I'm right in front of Buchiko.
You really get more bang for your buck at Big Bang Burger.
Won'tcha gimme your Desires?
Are you serious? Why would the Phantom Thieves target Alice?
Whaaat, they sent a calling card to Alice? Why!?
There's no way... The Phantom Thieves have got it all wrong.
I want Alice to step on me...
The Phantom Thieves are back!
Go, Phantom Thieves! We've been waiting for your return!
Man, what a party! This is so fun!
How do I get rid of all the Alice merch I've got at home?
Wow, I had no idea Alice was such a terrible person.
I dunno what's going on, but frankly I don't care anymore.
The rumors were true! The Phantom Thieves really are back!
I kind of feel sorry for Alice...
"New cosmetics in stock. You can't beat our prices!"
First that confession, now the Phantom Thieves' return... Will our country really be okay?
The Phantom Thieves are back!
Too many strange incidents are happening... What are we going to do?
Ugh, it's too hot. It's tiring me out...
What the... This store's got a 1 star rating? I ain't goin' there.
EMMA. List recommended travel goods.
Our taxes keep going up, but our wages don't. What a joke...
Isn't EMMA super useful?
There've been a lot of weird incidents recently, haven't there?
Oh, oh! I want pancakes!
All they ever talk about are idols. I'm tired of it.
Maybe I should apply at Big Bang Burger...
Where're you gonna go during summer break? We should go see the fireworks!
Maybe this AI will help Japan's economy make a comeback.
How many copies of “Prince of Nightmares” did you buy?
So the Phantom Thieves are back... Did you hear what they did to Alice?
I'm so obsessed with the Overlord, I forget to eat...
I hope Natsume's books get popular all over the world!
Being excited is fine, but they're going overboard. I don't get it.
Since Natsume likes Tanabata, I'm doing my decorations early this year!
I wonder if the Phantom Thieves will come to Sendai.
He's handsome AND talented... Natsume really is the total package.
Is it true that Natsume is a writer's grandson? He must've inherited his talent!
Hey, that's my book! Give it back!

I need to buy more copies of
“Prince of Nightmares”...
How dare the Phantom Thieves insult Natsume... That's unforgivable!
Oh, Natsume... Are you really going to be alright?
They don't know the first thing about him!
My days as a fan of the Phantom Thieves are over, starting today!
"Ostentatious swindler"... They've got some nerve.
See? I told you he wasn't all that!
The Phantom Thieves are here in Sendai!
So it was all a set up? I can't believe it...
Why did I buy so many copies of the same book...?
Y'know, I feel like I've seen all these lines in other books...
From today on, I'll be rooting for the Phantom Thieves!
The Phantom Thieves are amazing!
I hope he doesn't give up. I'd still like to read another book of his...
Why are the Phantom Thieves here in Sendai? What's going on?
Whoa... The Tanabata decorations are beautiful!
Let's ask EMMA. EMMA, list best gyutan places.
Things are weird lately. Did you hear about the Alice stuff?
I wonder what wish I should make for Tanabata...
It gets crowded during Tanabata season...
EMMA, what are the best Tanabata decorations?
I wonder if Date Masamune ate zunda mochi too?
Putting famous writers before politics... Kids these days.
It's hot out today. I'm exhausted...
Tanabata's even more beautiful at night.
I could see the Pacific Ocean from the observatory!
Freshly made! Get it while it's hot!
Mayor Hyodo's the only one who can protect our city.
Did you hear? The Phantom Thieves came to Sendai!
EMMA says we should vote for Hyodo, too.
Picking a candidate is such a pain. I'll just vote for Hyodo.
I'm sure she'll make living in this city easier.
A city without injustice... Like a paradise of pure white snow.
Mayor Hyodo will change Sapporo, and all of Japan, for the better.
*cough* *cough* I-I have to work harder... for the mayor's sake...
After the mayoral election, it'll be on to national politics.
No need to even think about it. All I have to do is vote for Mariko Hyodo.
Ngh... So sleepy. But I have to keep going, for Ms. Hyodo's sake...
Mariko Hyodo! Please vote Mariko Hyodo on election day!
Are the Phantom Thieves trying to destroy this city!?
I WANTED to be used! Stop getting in our way!
There's no reason for them to target the mayor!
We won't need the Phantom Thieves in our mayor's pure, pristine world!
Seeing all of these incidents happen is very worrying...
Whoa, the Phantom Thieves are in Sapporo too!? Are you serious?
I guess this is it for Hyodo.
Mariko Hyodo will NEVER lose to the Phantom Thieves!
This is exactly why you can't trust politicians.
Hyodo will definitely come back. I believe in her!
It's not the mayor's fault. She was doing the best she could...
Hiding something like this just to protect her position... She should be ashamed.
Oh! I've seen this sign before on the internet!
If even Mariko Hyodo steps down, who's going to lead Japan?
Is it just me, or is the world getting weirder and weirder by the day?
What? The Phantom Thieves came to Sapporo!?
Whenever I smell ramen, I can't help getting some for myself...
I hear Madicce is one of the top ten highest market value companies right now...
Welp. See you tomorrow.
Jingisukan, seafood bowl, or ramen... So many choices.
I hear you can get Hokkaido corn at Odori Park right now!
Wish they'd hold that fancy Snow Festival in the summertime.
People are acting way too desperate about this election.
Ugh, that campaign car really gets on my nerves!
Maybe I'll check out that club tonight...
That place has nothing but cute girls... It's practically heaven.
Maybe I'll check it out. I'll just have one drink...
Hey, have you heard the ghost story about this building?
*gulp* *gulp* ...Whew! That's a confidence boost!
So the Phantom Thieves were actually terrorists?
What the hell are the Phantom Thieves doing!?
Konoe-san is the only person we can rely on!
Whatever happened to that officer who was arrested...?
I'm going to buy stocks from Madicce to support him!
It's scary to think that there're terrorists around...
They're threatening Madicce...? What're they planning?
I wish I had a boss like Konoe-san...
Madicce started out in Osaka, but they're going to change the whole world!
Konoe-san is so sexy... I want him to give me bedroom eyes...
I can't make any decisions without EMMA...
I hope those good-for-nothing Phantom Thieves get captured soon.
Like stealing hearts wasn't enough. Now the Phantom Thieves are stealing EMMA!?
Who cares about the Phantom Thieves anyway!
We believe in you, Mr. Konoe!
Beat the Phantom Thieves' asses!
The hell is goin' on!?
The Phantom Thieves will regret this!
Rescue EMMA from the Phantom Thieves!
Who's the real tyrant here!?
No way will Mr. Konoe lose to some phantom nobodies!
Isn't everyone getting a bit too dependent on EMMA?
Well, the Phantom Thieves sure know how to get attention...
You oughta just delete weird apps like that.
Gotta learn to be more suspicious of stuff that's too convenient like that.
EMMA was so convenient, too... Talk about scary.
Takin' control of someone usin' an app... It's like a sci-fi movie.
The heck am I supposed to do without EMMA...
If it weren't for the Phantom Thieves... Sheesh. I don't even wanna think about it.
I betcha Madicce's stocks are gonna hit the floor...
What's gonna happen to this country now?
First it was Shido, now Konoe... Our leaders are droppin' like flies.
Hey EMMA... Oh wait, it ain't working right now.
EMMA's down right now? What am I supposed to do...?
I wish the economy was a little better...
It's so hot out every day... I can't stand it.
This store raised their prices too!? What a bummer...
Whoa! Did you see that cute girl just now?
Is it true that that celebrity is actually cheating on 9 people at once...?
I can't believe I've been eating flour-based stuff every day and I'm still not tired of it.
Dang... Summer break's almost over, huh...
I heard the light on the observation tower is where they check the forecast!
Here hun, I got you some candy.
Fried food and sake for lunch... This is the life.
Sir, why don't you come play?
I need another drink! Onto the next bar!
Hey... This serving feels smaller than before...
All right, let's motivate ourselves to work harder by eating some fugu!
Aw man, this thing is hilarious. I'm laughing so hard I'm crying!
Get some fresh, tasty crab right here at Crab Empire!
Damn... So the okonomiyaki DOES come with rice...

Alice, I love you...!
Marry me...!
Alice is so cute, I can't even...

Oh... I love it when
you talk down to me...

Harder, Queen Alice...!
Step on me harder...
Ohhh... I love you, Alice...

Ahhh... Being treated like
this really gets me going...

I will give Alice...
whatever she wants...
Alice must be an angel...
Queen Alice...
I only have eyes for Alice...
I'll follow Natsume... forever...

I wanna live in
Natsume's world...
Lord Ango...
This isn't love... It's my faith.
Lord Ango, please take my money...

Lord Ango...
You're so wonderful...

Ango Natsume's
book is the bible...
I need to spread the faith...

I'll devote my whole
self to Lord Ango...
Natsume is where it's at, man...

Your words are absolute,
Lord Ango...
I want to live in her Majesty Hyodo's ideal world...

I only believe in her
Majesty Hyodo...

Her Majesty will
decide everything...

Her Majesty Hyodo will make
everything perfect...

We'll be happy as long as we
follow her Majesty's words...

Her Majesty Hyodo is the
only thing on my mind...

Her Majesty Hyodo would never
do anything to hurt others...

Her Majesty's words will
bring us peace...
I am blessed to have her Majesty's presence all around me...
Her Majesty...
Lord Akira's my hero...
Our hero is the best there is...

You're out of your mind if you
oppose our superhero...

If we've got our hero,
we'll be all right.

We'll be okay if our superhero's
around.
Lord Akira's so badass...
Praise our hero!
Yeah, beat up those baddies!
Lord Akira only speaks the truth...

Our hero stands for justice...
No one can defy him!
We don't have to think anymore...
EMMA is always right...
We can leave it all up to EMMA...
Hey, EMMA... What should I do...?
I can't live without EMMA...
EMMA... Oh EMMA...
Let's just... listen to EMMA...

EMMA... Help me...
Take away my worries...
EMMA... Please guide me...
I'll do whatever you say, EMMA...
God... Please help us...
Take away my suffering...
Let's go to the Promised Land...
Save us... I beg of you...

I'll find salvation... In the
Promised Land...
Please... Please save us...
Oh... Mighty god...
Please help us, god... Guide us...
God... Please save us all...
Please guide us...

What'll it take to make them
stop bullying me...?

All this work... How will I ever
get this done in time?

Why...? What makes you wanna
hit me like that...?

It's my own fault for
following my dream when I
don't have any talent...
All this effort is pointless...
This isn't what I wanted out of life...
Why does this always happen to me!
Someone, guide me...
We don't have to think anymore...
EMMA is always right...
We can leave it all up to EMMA...
Hey, EMMA... What should I do...?
I can't live without EMMA...
EMMA has all the answers...
I need EMMA... I can't live without EMMA...
No... EMMA has to stay!
EMMA is ours...

I won't let anyone do
anything to EMMA...
EMMA is the reason I'm still alive...
Protect EMMA... Protect EMMA!
Stop! You can't hurt EMMA!
